oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Williams Jr. & Montgomery Gentry at the Starwood Amphitheatre
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Williams, Hank, Jr., 1949-; Montgomery Gentry (Musical group); Woodcuts (prints); Birds;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (yellow and blue on white) announcing Hank Williams Jr and Montgomery Gentry at the Starwood Amphitheatre on September 2. Poster features a woodcut of birds. The Starwood Amphitheatre was an outdoor music venue in Nashville, Tennessee from 1986 to 2006.
